ion that should be reconciled with the plan before other consumers depend on it.\n2. **Missing `relay` and `identity` TXT fields** -- `relay` is arguably v0.6 scope, but `identity` is needed for v0.4 discovery controller logic.\n3. **Extra `port` TXT field** -- harmless but not in the discovery contract.\n4. **No `bind_interfaces` parameter** on `MdnsSdBackend` -- the plan explicitly requires this in Chunk 1.\n\nAll Chunk 1 structural items (trait, events, types, fake backend, feature-gated real backend) are delivered. The dependency constraint (no reme-transport/reme-identity) is fully respected.</result>\n<usage><total_tokens>63970</total_tokens><tool_uses>12</tool_uses><duration_ms>81236</duration_ms></usage>\n</task-notification>\nFull transcript available at: /tmp/claude-1000/-home-leon0399-Projects-reme/36b495c0-95b9-49fc-8523-b911e74011a9/tasks/ae4e851575d868134.output",
